Vital Point to Capture?(38)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black's eye-space is really big.
\par However if White attacks step by step, he can capture Black.
\par
\par The first and third move are obvious and the fifth is the deciding move.
\par }
