Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It looks common but capturing the Black stone with White 1 and 3 is the only way to capture Black.
\par
\par Now Black can't defend against White A and B at the same time.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
