Dia. 02 No Follow up
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par There is death in the hane?
\par If White is using that proverb now at plays hane at 1, Black connects at 2 and then White has no follow up.
\par
\par If White plays the placement at 3, Black cuts with 4 and nothing works anymore.
\par }
